abstract: Neil Genzlinger reviews TV One network series Here We Go Again,  starring LeToya Luckett.

headline.main: Review: ‘Here We Go Again,’ a Tradition of Teenage Moms

snippet: A new series on TV One follows two women who became mothers at 16, and their concerns for a daughter in the newest generation.
lead_paragraph: A new series on TV One follows two women who became mothers at 16, and their concerns for a daughter in the newest generation.
